  <body>
    <main><%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %></main>
    <main class="help-section">
      <h1>Help</h1>
      <h2>How to add your favorite movie/ tv show on the dashboard</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Click the add show</li>
        <li>Enter the name of the movie/tv show you want to review.</li>
        <li>
          Select tv if what you are searching is a tv show otherwise select
          movie.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <h2>How to add a review</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Select the movie/ tv show you want to rate.</li>
        <li>Click the add reviews button.</li>
        <li>Add your review on the field.</li>
        <li>Click the "Post Review" button to add the review.</li>
      </ol>
      <h2>How to see the reviews</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Select the movie/ tv show you want to rate.</li>
        <li>Click the "See reviews" button.</li>
      </ol>
    </main>
